                                      @Nullable
                                      IFactorTable oldFactorTable,
                                      java.util.ArrayList<Variable> constantVariables,
                                      int[] constantIndices)
        Description copied from class: Factor
        Replaces factor function conditioned on a set of variables with fixed values that have already been removed from the factor. This should only be called from within Factor.removeFixedVariables().

        This is invoked after the fixed value variables have already been disconnected from the factor, but before the factor function has been replaced.
